--- SCENARIO: herson reveals which contested civs were banned and who had ranked them ---
# Alice and Bob both rank Lincoln first. Lincoln is contested, so the resolver bans it and both fall
# through to their next pick. When the draft closes the status explains the resolution: the banned
# civ plus which players had it and at what priority.

--- CHAT ---
alice: /lobby herson
bob: /register

--- DM (alice) ---
alice: /leaders
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">
--- DM (bob) ---
bob: /leaders
ambotorix: <button "{leader}">

--- CHAT ---
alice: /start
ambotorix: @alice* @bob* <backlink>
ambotorix:

--- DM (alice) ---
ambotorix: *Herson draft*
alice: 1. lincoln 2. curtin 3. montezuma 4. hammurabi
ambotorix: *Picks recorded*

--- DM (bob) ---
ambotorix: *Herson draft*
bob: 1. lincoln 2. pedro 3. basil 4. theodora
ambotorix: *Picks recorded*

--- CHAT ---
ambotorix: 📥 All picks are in* <backlink>
ambotorix: <image *resolved*> <backlink>   # picks revealed as a portrait image
ambotorix: <status *Status: done*Contested (banned):*America Abraham Lincoln*@alice (#1)*@bob (#1)*>
ambotorix:
